[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0340","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0340.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0169","title":"NFS 虚假UID认证绕过漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）协议存在认证缺陷，其基于 UID（用户 ID）的访问控制机制未对客户端身份进行有效验证。远程攻击者无需合法凭据，仅需在 NFS 请求中伪造特权用户（如 root）的 UID 值，即可绕过文件权限检查，实现对目标系统上任意文件的读取与写入操作。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 NFS 服务实现，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，可导致敏感数据泄露、系统文件篡改乃至完全控制服务器。由于 NFS 协议设计阶段未内置强认证机制，此问题属于架构性安全缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0169"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01","updated":"1997-07-01","remediation":"升级 NFS 服务端至 NFSv4 版本，配置 /etc/exports 中启用 root_squash 和 all_squash 选项强制将远程用户映射为匿名用户，避免直接绕过权限检查；同时使用 sec=krb5 或 sec=krb5p 启用 Kerberos 认证，防止客户端伪造 UID/GID。在无法升级的场景下，应在防火墙层面限制 NFS 端口（2049/TCP/UDP）仅允许受信 IP 段访问，并使用 exports 的 rw/ro 和 subnet 限制作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0340.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0783","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0783.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0526","title":"X 服务器 Xhost + 访问控制开启漏洞（CVE-1999-0526)","description":"某些 X 服务器产品默认配置不安全，通过 'xhost +' 命令开启了访问控制，导致任何远程 X 客户端均可连接到服务器。这种配置允许攻击者监控键盘输入或注入 X 事件，通常足以获取运行 X 服务器的用户权限。该漏洞源于便捷性考虑下的不安全配置，不是严格控制允许主机列表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0526"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-01","updated":"1997-07-01","remediation":"禁用 xhost + 配置，使用 Xauthority 机制配置安全密钥文件，SSH 用户可将允许主机列表设置为 127.0.0.1 以确保隧道安全。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T04:55:44.767932791+00:00","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/704969"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0783.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0095","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0095.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0033","title":"Sun Solaris at 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun 系统的 at 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于对用户输入数据长度校验不严，本地攻击者可向 at 程序提交特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 SunOS、UnixWare、Open Desktop、OpenServer 等多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。仅需本地账户即可利用，无需认证。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0033"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.453","remediation":"立即升级 Sun Solaris 至 2.5.1 及以上安全补丁版本，或安装 Sun 发布的对应安全补丁（如 105830-xx 系列）。对于 UnixWare/OpenServer 等受影响系统，升级至厂商修复版本。临时缓解措施：移除 at 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/at），或通过编辑 cron.allow/at.allow 文件严格限制可执行 at 命令的用户白名单。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0033"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0095.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0197","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0197.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0083","title":"SGI IRIX FTP 文件描述符泄露漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统的 FTP 服务中存在文件描述符泄露漏洞，`getcwd()` 函数在处理 FTP 请求时未能正确关闭文件描述符，导致系统文件描述符资源被逐步耗尽。远程攻击者可通过多次发送特定 FTP 命令触发此漏洞，造成 FTP 服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0083"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.437","remediation":"建议升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.3 及以上版本（含 SGI 安全补丁 19970701-01-P），修复 FTP 守护进程 getcwd() 文件描述符泄漏问题。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 FTP 行并重启 inetd 以禁用匿名 FTP，或在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 21 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0197.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0461","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0461.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0275","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 DNS Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 DNS 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标系统的 UDP 53 端口发送大量超长字符数据包，导致 DNS 服务耗尽系统资源而崩溃拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击条件简单，仅需网络可达即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0275"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.227","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本安全更新，限制仅允许信任源 IP 访问 DNS 服务端口 53，在防火墙层面启用速率限制和连接数控制以缓解 DNS 泛洪攻击。建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0275","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0275","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0275.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w59j-5972-p7cr/GHSA-w59j-5972-p7cr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_dns_flood.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0461.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0461.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0461.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0372","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0372.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0189","title":"Sun Solaris rpcbind 服务远程未授权访问漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中的 rpcbind 服务默认监听在 UDP 端口 111，同时会动态绑定到其他高位 UDP 端口。由于网络管理员通常仅过滤标准端口 111，而未对高位 UDP 端口实施访问控制策略，导致远程攻击者可绕过防火墙过滤规则直接访问 rpcbind 服务，进而获取系统 RPC 程序信息映射，为后续远程攻击提供信息支撑。该漏洞影响所有使用 rpcbind 的 Solaris 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0189"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.400","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #142 中对应 Solaris 版本的补丁（覆盖 Solaris 2.3~2.5.1）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制 rpcbind 仅允许 UDP 111 端口通行，并添加规则阻断高位 UDP 端口的入站流量；同时可在 /etc/system 中配置 rpcbind 仅绑定已知端口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/142"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0372.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0294","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0294.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0144","title":"Dan Bernstein QMail 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"QMail 1.0 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 SMTP 协议的 RCPT 命令指定大量收件人地址，导致 QMail 在处理过程中消耗过多系统资源（CPU 与内存），最终造成邮件服务瘫痪。该漏洞影响 Dan Bernstein QMail 1.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分为 2.1，危害等级低。官方建议升级至 QMail 1.03 或更高版本进行修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0144"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.470","remediation":"升级到 netqmail 1.06 或应用 qmail-1.03 的 RCPT DoS 补丁；在 qmail-smtpd 中设置软限制参数 `MAXRCPTS`（如设为 100），限制单次 SMTP 会话的收件人数量；同时启用 `rcpthosts` 和 `morercpthosts` 控制邮件转发，防止被滥用为拒绝服务攻击的反射点。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cr.yp.to/qmail/venema.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319024&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319029&w=2","http://www.ornl.gov/its/archives/mailing-lists/qmail/1997/06/threads.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2237","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/208","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20562","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0144","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0144.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-78g5-jc8q-wgq5/GHSA-78g5-jc8q-wgq5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2237/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0144.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0294.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0413","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0413.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0227","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 LSA/LSARPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的本地安全认证子系统服务（LSASS.EXE）在处理 LSA/LSARPC 请求时存在访问冲突漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，触发 LSASS.EXE 进程崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，但无法实现远程代码执行或提权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0227"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.290","remediation":"建议升级至受支持版本的 Windows（Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2019/2022 等），Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持且不再发布安全更新。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上阻止 TCP 135 (RPC) 和 139 (NetBIOS) 端口的入站连接，限制 LSARPC 接口的远程访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ154087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0227","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80917/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87f50d43-aca9-4ba6-b704-6b3b4ebdaad2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0413.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0468","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0468.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0281","title":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 URL长路径拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 2.0 及 3.0 版本存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长 URL 请求，导致 IIS 服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成服务不可用。该漏洞无需身份认证即可触发，攻击门槛低，影响运行 IIS 2.0/3.0 的 Windows NT 系统。由于年代久远，微软已停止支持相关版本，建议升级至更高版本 IIS。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0281"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.960","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft IIS 4.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中启用 URL 长度限制（设置 MaxClientRequestBuffer 注册表值为 4096 字节），并在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务 80/443 端口的异常长 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0281","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20802","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0281.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0281","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0281.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0281.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5a605876-602f-4a7d-96cb-b788c024c2a8.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0281.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0468.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0468.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0468.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1156","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1156.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0799","title":"BSD bootpd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"bootpd（Bootstrap Protocol Daemon）2.4.3 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的包含超长引导文件路径的 DHCP/BOOTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，可能造成远程代码执行或服务崩溃。该漏洞影响运行 bootpd 服务的各类 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0799"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.920","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 bootpd 2.4.3 及更早版本中，由于对引导文件位置参数长度缺乏有效校验，攻击者可通过提交超长 boot file 路径触发缓冲区溢出，实现远程代码执行，CVSS v2.0 评分 10.0，危害极高。建议立即升级 bootpd 至 2.4.4 或更高版本（如已停止维护，应彻底禁用 bootpd 服务）；如业务仍依赖 BOOTP 协议，应迁移至 DHCP 服务（如 isc-dhcp-server），并在防火墙上限制 UDP 端口 67/68 的访问来源。对于无法立即升级的遗留系统，可在服务启动参数中限制配置文件路径长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0799","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fec368cf82886628cf7251fa55925507d7e50c60/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0799.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0799","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0799.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0799.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cvq9-5xpv-rx24/GHSA-cvq9-5xpv-rx24.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0799.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/324/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1156.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0090","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0034","title":"Perl suidperl 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"suidperl（sperl）是 Perl 中用于执行 SUID 权限脚本的辅助程序，其在处理用户输入时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向目标系统提交特制的 Perl 脚本参数触发该溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Perl 4.x 及 5.x 版本，涉及 BSD/OS、RedHat、SGI 等多个操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0034"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.680","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004 或更高版本以修复 suidperl 缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可移除 suidperl 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl），并改用 sudo 机制替代 setuid 脚本执行。长期建议彻底废弃 suidperl，使用常规 Perl 解释器配合 sudo 调用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0034","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0034.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp.json","https://github.com/briandfoy/cpan-security-advisory/blob/b45d5ed44c1ca4a46a9138ebed1f2bec6deb0956/TO_DO","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0099","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0035","title":"多厂商 Unix ftpd 信号处理竞态条件漏洞","description":"ftpd 守护进程的信号处理例程中存在条件竞争漏洞（Race Condition），攻击者可利用信号处理时序差绕过文件访问控制，实现任意文件读取或写入。该漏洞影响多个 UNIX 系统中的 ftpd 实现，攻击者需与目标建立 FTP 连接并在特定操作窗口内触发竞态条件以完成利用，CVSS 评分 5.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0035"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.893","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了信号处理例程中的条件竞争问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/wu-ftpd）或替换为 vsftpd/ProFTPD 等更安全的 FTP 守护进程。在不必要的情况下，可通过防火墙限制对 21 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0035"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0096","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0036","title":"SGI IRIX login 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 及之前版本中的 /bin/login 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。当 LOCKOUT 参数设置为非零值时，攻击者可通过精心构造的输入触发缓冲区溢出，以 root 权限创建或破坏系统文件，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，利用门槛较低，危害严重。SGI 已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0036"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.110","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 1997 年 5 月安全公告 19970508-02-PX 提供的修补补丁。临时缓解措施：在 /etc/default/login 配置文件中将 LOCKOUT 参数设为 0 并重启 login 服务。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止技术支持多年，建议尽快迁移至仍受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-106.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/990","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/557","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19310","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0036","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/dcc6735c9c3e50e93de820fa1ac9c54ecf6b2577/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0036.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0163","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0163.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0064","title":"IBM AIX lquerylv 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统的 lquerylv 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过向该程序发送精心构造的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 多个版本，需要本地用户身份才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0064"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.583","remediation":"立即安装 IBM AIX APAR IX73924 安全补丁，或升级至 AIX 4.2.1 及以上版本。若无法立即打补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lquerylv` 移除该程序的 setuid 位，以阻止本地普通用户通过此漏洞获取 root 权限；同时限制不可信用户的本地访问权限作为深度防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418428&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/335","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0064","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0064.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972